profile:
Business Address: 1957 Avenue Rd., Toronto, Ontario, M5M 4A1, Canada
When your technology needs repair in the North York area of Toronto, uBreakiFix Avenue Road is your solution.

We are conveniently located in the heart of Toronto, just off highway 401 at the Avenue Road south exit. We are on the east side of Avenue Road, nestled between Haddington and Felbrigg. Right across the street from uBreakiFix is the famous Lobster Trap and a Starbucks only a couple blocks down the road. This vibrant area is well known for many boutiques and restaurants such as Drums N’ Flats and Bistro on Avenue. If you’re looking for additional shopping and entertainment options, Yorkdale Mall is only a few kilometres away.

uBreakiFix Avenue Road is your one stop shop for all your gadget repair needs. Our team of expert technicians is ready to provide their services to the Toronto community. Our excellent customer service and one of the fastest repair turn around times in the industry make uBreakiFIx Avenue Road the number one option in the area for all repairs.

We will make sure you have your device back as soon as possible. We begin by running a free diagnostic to identify any issue your device might have. Once the problem is identified, we will get started with the repair.

How long will your repair take? We strive for same day repairs, and in some instances- particularly with certain phone fixes – we get them done in 30 minutes or less.

From broken cell phone screens to soaked devices, our friendly and knowledgeable technicians have got it all covered, backed with our 90-day nationwide warranty on all repairs! We fix many brands including Apple, Blackberry, Samsung, LG, Sony, Motorola and more. We also take care of your XBOX, Playstation, Macs (or other type of computer) and iPads (or other Tablets).

Call to set up an appointment or book online – Hey, even simply drop your iPhone off without notice on the way to Downtown, Yorkdale Mall, or Yonge and Eglinton.



We are here for you and look forward to helping you!
